Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.78,0:00:09.23,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:12.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.88,0:00:16.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.05,0:00:24.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.85,0:00:34.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.73,0:00:41.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.95,0:00:48.89,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.91,0:00:56.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.51,0:01:03.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.43,0:01:07.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.43,0:01:10.41,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:14.58,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.60,0:01:18.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:21.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.15,0:01:25.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.66,0:01:29.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.37,0:01:32.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.66,0:01:35.65,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.67,0:01:41.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.42,0:01:49.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.08,0:02:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do what you want with the Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.38,0:02:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get a new ship and\Nmove on to the seas ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, bye, Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.95,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lose yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.41,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you waver, who can we trust?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.63,0:03:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's vacate the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't come back... to this ship, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.48,0:03:32.48,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Severe Shock Hits the City\Nof Water! Iceberg Targeted!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was the first to find him?\NPlease let us question them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:42.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they connected with the\Nannihilation of Franky House?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us the latest developments!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.13,0:03:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you hear about the incident\Nat the shipbuilding island?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.63,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it true that he died?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.47,0:03:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be Franky who did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This happened because they left him at large!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.52,0:03:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's also a strong chance it was\Ndone by pirates who visit the shipyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.64,0:04:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I heard that there was an\Nexplosion at the cape late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.98,0:04:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that related to this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.94,0:04:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know, but there are many pirates\Nwho got beaten up by the foremen, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.55,0:04:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is where you guys were...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We went to the trouble of getting a room\Nat this inn and yet no one's in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you all couldn't sleep, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.32,0:04:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.57,0:04:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd you go, Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.62,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm... I kept a lookout at\Nthe rocky cape all night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.71,0:05:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thinking that Robin-chan might come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.67,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder where she went...\Nwithout saying anything to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been nothing but trouble\Nsince we got to this island.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had our money stolen, and moreover,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,look what happened with Usopp...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's badly wounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.82,0:05:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's running a fever\Nby now and can't even move!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.28,0:05:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.33,0:05:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.92,0:05:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm gonna wander around\Ntown looking for her today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.76,0:05:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have specific\Nplaces in mind to check,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but in any case, it's certain that\Nshe's somewhere in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:08.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make this inn the place to\Nmeet up if something happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go look for her, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Well, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.57,0:06:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.78,0:06:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! The whole\Ntown is talking about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Last night, Iceberg-san\Nfrom the shipyard was...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san was shot at his home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.80,0:06:32.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Was he killed?!\N--Well, hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't someone who\Nmakes enemies of people!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.14,0:06:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec. Calm down, Paulie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.80,0:06:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Iceberg-san was found covered\Nin blood in his room this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still in a coma, so he's\Nunconscious right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.23,0:06:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, come to the\Nmain office immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.82,0:07:02.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu! Where's Paulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just called him. He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.87,0:07:06.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.41,0:07:10.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Newspaper reporters are already here\Nand it's quite an uproar outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.00,0:07:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...even though we're the ones who\Nwant to know what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.34,0:07:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although they tore up the whole office,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:20.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no trace of money\Nor valuables being stolen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.01,0:07:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't for robbery, who'd have\Na reason to shoot Iceberg-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.64,0:07:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, we're in big trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.23,0:07:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole town is in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.28,0:07:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to him,\Nthe Galley-La Company--
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.82,0:07:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as Water Seven-- will be finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:08:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor... How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was shot twice from the front,\Nand thrice from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened in that room\Nlast night, but it sure was brutal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the forensics,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no trace of locks being\Npicked anywhere in the building.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.87,0:08:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The incident occurred in a\Nroom no one could've entered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing found in the room\Nwas a commonplace mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.30,0:08:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice pops was?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.34,0:08:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that he's unconscious right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thinks the world of him. Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.56,0:08:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that, Nami-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.27,0:08:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who helped us yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.48,0:09:00.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the president of the shipbuilding\Ncompany and the mayor of Water Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like he's quite a big shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You couldn't come up with a\Nbigger incident than this in this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.99,0:09:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go check.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.04,0:09:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Luffy! I'm coming, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.46,0:09:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's go look for Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.84,0:09:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait a little while and\Nsee how things turn out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.64,0:09:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Extra edition! Extra! Extra!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Water Seven's hero-- our mayor,\NIceberg-san-- fell victim to an assassin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:38.75,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Iceberg Falls Victim to Assassin"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.77,0:09:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a news flash about the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Iceberg-san okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.74,0:09:47.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible. How could this happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.78,0:09:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.20,0:09:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the culprit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.95,0:09:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The paper doesn't have any clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.75,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, paper guy! This doesn't have\Nthe crucial piece of information!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.96,0:09:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.46,0:10:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a vicious attack... It must be pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.67,0:10:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd sure like for us to catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.30,0:10:08.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were pirates who went on a\Nrampage at Dock #1 yesterday, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.80,0:10:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mikazuki gang?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be shocking, but I think it\Nmight be the government's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lulu, what're you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.98,0:10:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about Corgy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.27,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time he comes to talk to Iceberg-san,\Nhe gets turned down and goes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.20,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky must be the culprit after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.99,0:10:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it was all about,\Nbut he must've done it out of spite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.66,0:10:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain about the government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:40.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If someone hears, you'll pay for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the goal of this unforgivable\Nculprit to gain wealth or power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.38,0:10:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this assassin who\Ndisappeared without a trace?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.13,0:10:50.33,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,"Mr. Iceberg Falls Victim to Assassin"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.35,0:10:58.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell did it?! I'm not\Ngonna let him get away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.35,0:11:01.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for riding the train.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.15,0:11:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be arriving at Blue Station in\Nthe City of Water, Water Seven, soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.61,0:11:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Paulie-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paulie-san! Please give us\Na statement on the incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.78,0:11:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you told before you came here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.87,0:11:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up. Get out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What explanation did your company give you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.33,0:11:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a statement!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.92,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you deaf? I told you to get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hasn't there been any trouble that could have\Ncaused someone to target Mr. Iceberg's life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.92,0:12:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything that comes to your mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.30,0:12:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any trouble with pirates?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Paulie-san! Tell us...\N--I said get out of my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.76,0:12:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dumbasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! I'm right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Hurry, Yagara!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.61,0:12:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Yagara-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:37.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, please get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.12,0:12:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's talking about Iceberg-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.46,0:12:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's true that he was attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.80,0:12:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Even if we go to the shipyard,\Nwe may not be able to see him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.30,0:12:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's go to pops' house.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.26,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that his private residence\Nis inside the main office.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.01,0:13:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Because I'm weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That large amount of money... They stole it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.72,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were finally about to have Merry repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.16,0:14:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.37,0:14:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.78,0:14:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiwi... Mozu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Am I dreaming?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.87,0:14:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.20,0:14:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is, without a doubt,\Nthe place where Franky House was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.38,0:14:55.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...terrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:15:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who did this while I was gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... It must be them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.74,0:15:24.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you, Straw Hat Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.45,0:15:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did this as retaliation for my\Nstealing your 200 million Berries?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do this to\Nmy precious underlings?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.63,0:15:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How cold-blooded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.34,0:15:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.26,0:15:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Bro Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.05,0:15:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.05,0:15:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you guys are okay? Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.69,0:15:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had a terrible time.\NThose guys are really crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We want you to get revenge for us at any cost,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.07,0:16:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we've been spying on\Nthe Straw Hats' movements.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We saw them going into an inn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From there, they headed to the\Nshipbuilding island a bit ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.04,0:16:13.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet they went to the place\Nthey went yesterday, Dock #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.50,0:16:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.51,0:16:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat Luffy... I'll crush you without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.90,0:16:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma! Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The wind is blowing like crazy! Hey, Grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crazy wind! Crazy wind!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.03,0:16:51.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Crazy wind!\N--Don't romp around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.21,0:16:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a southern wind... Karock, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.88,0:17:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The waves are becoming quite rough, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.72,0:17:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands, the sea train service\Nwill have to be stopped tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.73,0:17:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chimney! Gonbe! Get ready\Nto go back to the island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.98,0:17:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.90,0:17:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Water Seven\NWeather Forecasting Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.59,0:17:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An Aqua Laguna warning has just\Nbeen issued for the entire island.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Its arrival time at Water Seven is\Nestimated to be after midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah... It's that time of the year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was preoccupied with Iceberg-san's incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:57.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Aqua Laguna is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.56,0:17:59.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let those who didn't hear\Nthe warning yet know!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.48,0:18:02.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No more working today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.20,0:18:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.28,0:18:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.32,0:18:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that broadcast about?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it about? Of course it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.79,0:18:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, are you a traveler?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.37,0:18:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you came here at a bad time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.63,0:18:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.09,0:18:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aqua Laguna is a storm surge.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A storm surge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:26.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Make sure you\Nevacuate to high ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.72,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This town will be submerged in the sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.64,0:18:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The town will be submerged...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.98,0:18:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It's not going\Nto happen right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.64,0:18:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the forecast, it'll be\Nhere around midnight tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.86,0:18:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this happens every year. Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.53,0:18:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.07,0:18:45.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be submerged in the sea?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! This place will sink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.32,0:18:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like it. At any rate,\Nlet's hurry and find Robin-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.99,0:18:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.04,0:18:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, where should we look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.58,0:19:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... where would she be likely to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.88,0:19:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.97,0:19:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruins, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There probably aren't any here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anywhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.68,0:19:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.72,0:19:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what does she like?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.93,0:19:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--That'd be ruins!\N--You keep saying that!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do you know what else she likes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.73,0:19:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking because I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't get in front of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.32,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that we don't know\Nanything about Robin-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please tell us something!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.63,0:19:42.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Iceberg-san!\N--What the hell happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.79,0:19:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.46,0:19:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't enter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:52.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll have to see Ice pops sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, excuse me. Do you know where\Nthe entrance to the main office is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:20:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's no use. You go in through Dock #1,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.56,0:20:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but only concerned parties and\Ncertain reporters are allowed inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just you guys. Everyone is so\Nworried that they can't just sit and wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.58,0:20:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all this fuss about?\NLots of people are here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.12,0:20:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the bigger the audience, the better.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.63,0:20:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! This rhythm is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.59,0:20:34.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...! Oh, no...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:35.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why at a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys! Did you just call my name?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:42.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't! Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where?! Where is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! He's over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.03,0:20:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--He's here!\N--Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.90,0:20:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Yow!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.62,0:20:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come now, don't be shy, ask me my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.12,0:20:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't wanna ask! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who attacked\NIceberg-san, aren't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?! He did it?!\N--It's gotta be him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.96,0:21:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone from this island!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.96,0:21:09.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be sent to the gallows, you punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.34,0:21:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... what noisy flies...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.47,0:21:17.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the No. 1 super guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.64,0:21:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The face of the Water Seven underworld!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.98,0:21:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! People call me... wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.86,0:21:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Franky!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.49,0:21:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:09.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.07,0:22:12.59,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:18.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.20,0:22:20.47,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.49,0:22:23.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.66,0:22:29.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:31.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.01,0:22:34.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:37.74,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.76,0:22:40.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:43.62,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.64,0:22:46.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.48,0:22:52.13,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.15,0:22:54.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:57.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.78,0:23:00.35,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.37,0:23:08.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.09,0:23:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.92,0:23:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that guy is Franky?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.21,0:23:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you, bikini guy! I won't\Nbe happy until I beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore.\NNo one can stop me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.89,0:23:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.51,0:23:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa! What the hell?!\NHe breathed fire! That's kinda cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.48,0:23:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me he's got Devil Fruit powers?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.81,0:23:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.10,0:23:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Gum-Gum Human vs. Fire-breathing Cyborg"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.19,0:23:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
